## CI Fix (fake-ts stack restack)
`test_total_storage_size_is_project_scoped` used literal strings ('project-call',
'other-project-call') as call ids. ClickHouse requires call ids to be UUIDs
(require_uuid -> CHValidationError: Invalid UUID), so the test failed on the real
backend (passed on the fake which skips UUID validation). Switched to str(uuid.uuid4()).

